Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.02,0:01:03.06,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,0)}月亮轻声低语
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.81,0:01:08.11,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}用无人听到的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.03,0:01:12.36,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}编织潮涨潮落
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.32,0:01:16.32,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}记忆中的景色无法消失
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.79,0:01:22.08,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}繁星密集地标记
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.42,0:01:26.79,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}用无人理解的文字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.25,0:01:31.88,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}无限的语言卷成漩涡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.18,0:01:36.55,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}孕育出千亿本书
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.56,0:01:44.02,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}天空对我太宽广
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.48,0:01:48.94,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}时间对我太迅速
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.07,0:01:54.61,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}一无所知地空虚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.11,0:01:58.03,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}聚集的语言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.78,0:02:02.00,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}也只会在土地中枯朽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.50,0:02:08.79,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}即便如此我仍喊叫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.05,0:02:13.92,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}莫名地提高声音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.34,0:02:19.10,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}至少要响彻天的彼端
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.81,0:02:24.68,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,400,3000,4000)}太阳会因此升起吧


Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.99,0:00:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那座城堡？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.99,0:00:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 那就是米修堡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里曾经有人居住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.83,0:00:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.87,0:00:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.70,0:00:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濒临毁灭的世界…么


